    "long_instructions": "#### Investigate\r\n\r\nBrendan discovered this <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-waveform\" style=\"color: #F3DF55; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Waterfall </span> effect. He wondered if we could play it at the same time as the <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-waveform\" style=\"color: #F3DF55; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Chime </span> effects at the end!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/12d5e433c9f1a8ed8fd9f28a1dcadc4d-image-1743108126547.png)\r\n\r\nTry to recreate the code above on your own, or follow the step-by-step instructions below:\r\n\r\n1) Drag out a <code style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 148, 202); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">play together</code> block [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-second-block)\r\n2) Rearrange your code so the repeat block with the <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-waveform\" style=\"color: #F3DF55; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Chime </span> effects is inside the block. [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=id:chimes_workspace)\r\n3) Add the play block with the <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-waveform\" style=\"color: #F3DF55; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Waterfall </span> effect so it plays at the same time as the chimes. [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-first-block)\r\n\r\n> If you're stuck, try clicking the <i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i> icons for hints!",
